collections.name: The Watchers
collections.description:
The Watchers,
are not just observers. They are ancient beings, cloaked in the lunar dust, who have watched humanity for millennia. From their obsidian city on the moon's far side, they have meticulously collected the tapestry of human knowledge, their eyes like cold, calculating stars.

This NFT collection represents a piece of their watchful gaze. Each NFT grants you access to a unique staking reward system, offering Mbro coins as a reward for your contribution to the Watchers' grand design.

These are not just NFTs, they are keys to a hidden world. By holding a Watcher NFT, you become a part of the ancient conspiracy, a silent participant in the harvesting of human knowledge.

Join the Watchers and unlock the secrets of the moon.

The future is being written, and you can be a part of it.

Will you answer the call?

Collectors can build their own virtual fleets, showcasing their favorite ship types and participating in a thriving community of space explorers.

collections.name: Circle by Iba
collections.description:
Iba (pronounced e-bah) is an anonymous artist creating a limited number of evocative, AI-enhanced works that explore the delicate balance between human creativity and machine precision. Guided by the belief that art should speak for itself, Iba remains intentionally anonymous—inviting viewers to engage with each piece free from narrative or identity.

Iba’s debut collection, Circle by Iba, includes nine unique pieces, each meticulously crafted and enhanced by AI. Every artwork in the collection is minted only once as an NFT, ensuring true digital scarcity and permanence. Circle by Iba reflects on cycles, connections, and the unseen forces that shape us, offering a meditative visual experience that is both timeless and modern.

This collection is a quiet invitation—to pause, observe, and connect with art in its purest form.

Iba reserves all rights.

collections.name: Gemmae noctis
collections.description:
Beneath the vast, star-strewn sky, where the aurora dances in ethereal waves, I find the canvas. As a dedicated nightscape photographer, I chase the beauty of the unseen world—one that only reveals itself under the cover of darkness. 
The journey requires patience and endurance, countless hours in frigid, desolate landscapes to capture the fleeting magic of the night. From the ghostly glow of the northern lights to the silent brilliance of a star-filled expanse, the work is a testament to the perseverance and passion required to bring the nocturnal wonders to life. 
Through photos and mesmerizing time-lapse videos, I invite viewers into a realm where time slows, shadows stretch, and the cosmos speaks in colors and light.
